data.description: No MUD or PID. Ready for immediate move in.  Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom,3 bathroom home nestled in the desirable Gateway Park community. This residence beautifully combines modern design with functional living spaces, offering a comfortable and luxurious lifestyle. Upon entering, you'll immediately appreciate the open floorplan, fostering a sense of spaciousness and connectivity throughout the main living areas. The heart of the home, the kitchen, adorned with elegant granite countertops, it offers not only a visually appealing space but also a highly functional one. The stainless steel appliances add a touch of modernity. The split primary bedroom layout ensures privacy and tranquility, featuring double sinks,  garden tub, ideal for unwinding after a long day, as well as a separate shower for a refreshing start to your mornings.  Don't miss the chance to make this remarkable property your own.
